headline: Has Ralph Lauren’s Global Expansion Fueled a Sustainable 69% Rally in 2025?
summary: Curious if Ralph Lauren stock is worth the premium price tag or hiding untapped value? Let’s break down what recent performance and fundamentals are telling us. The stock has soared, gaining 12.2% in the past week, 60.3% year-to-date, and an impressive 69.0% over the last twelve months. This suggests significant changes in investor sentiment, whether due to growth prospects or shifting risk perceptions.
